cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

The paper deals with object detection from point clouds, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed framework involves the use of neural networks for proposal generation and bounding box estimation, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of point-wise features, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL).
